Chess/PGN/EPD version 0.03
==========================

CHESS::PGN::EPD - Perl extension to convert an array moves in PGN standard notation, to
EPD form. See POD and Changes file for details.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Chess::PGN::Moves
Chess::PGN::PGNParser (useless without, not actually required though...)

